  %section.how-to
    %h2 How to install
    %p
      Installing artoo with ardrone support is pretty easy using ruby gems.
    :markdown
          :::bash
          gem install artoo-spark

    %h2 How to use
    %p This small program lets you turn on or off a LED for every 1 sec.

    :markdown
          :::ruby

          require 'artoo'

          connection :spark, :adaptor => :spark, :access_token => 'XYZABC123'
          device :led, :driver => :led, :pin => 'D0'

          work do
            every(1.second) do
              led.toggle
            end
          end
    
